<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=6769&amp;p=29430#p29430"><![CDATA[
Hi shpkong. <br /><br />Really wild designs on the net, that can be a custom menu image.<br /><br />Here is what I was talking about before.<br />Picture is example about the white text on white menu background, with possible tint option on/off.<br />It might not be the best way to get effect. Looks a bit muddy.<br />You would need to make extra search pattern mask 47, with red at 200/255.<br />I put this text in Skin 1 folder:<br /><br /><br />OPTION TINTED=&quot;Tinted custom Image&quot;,0,CUSTOM_IMAGE_LEFT,0<br /><br /><br />[TINTED AND CUSTOM_IMAGE_LEFT AND COLOR_BLACK OR COLOR_GREEN OR COLOR_BLUE OR COLOR_RED OR COLOR_CUSTOM]<br />Main_pattern_mask=#C80000<br />Main_pattern_search_mask=#C80000<br />Main_pattern_jump_mask=#C80000<br />Search_pattern_mask=47<br /><br /><br />For Skin 2 folder with the round corners, another main pattern mask 48, with 200/255 red,<br />would need to be made as well:<br /><br />[TINTED AND CUSTOM_IMAGE_LEFT AND COLOR_BLACK OR COLOR_GREEN OR COLOR_BLUE OR COLOR_RED OR COLOR_CUSTOM]<br />Main_pattern_mask=48<br />Main_pattern_search_mask=48<br />Main_pattern_jump_mask=48<br />Search_pattern_mask=47<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=856">juniper7</a> — Mon Sep 19, 2016 2:00 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
</entry>
